    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/a8c97fecd84b391a3e1bc69ccc7f5432.poster.avif?t=1765825394\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/a8c97fecd84b391a3e1bc69ccc7f5432.webm?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/a8c97fecd84b391a3e1bc69ccc7f5432.mp4?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Water Delivery》是一款第一人称恐怖体验游戏，你在游戏中扮演一个送水工。你将乘坐送水车，从一户人家送到另一户人家。你需要送去装满水的水壶，找到并归还空水壶，并收取所有的付款。你能完成你晚上的最后一趟路线吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特性:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 乘坐送水车，从一户人家送到另一户人家，一边听着收音机里的Lo-Fi节拍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从卡车后部拿起装满水的水壶，将它们送到投递点。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在房子和周围的物业中寻找所有的空水壶，并将它们归还给卡车。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 当你完成每项工作时，一定要从房主那里收取钱款。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在此过程中，你将揭开困扰这个农村社区的黑暗之谜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 游戏有多个结局，取决于你做出的选择和你发现的事物。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/fcb47626eee0a0e0d4d5a789ec5d3baa.poster.avif?t=1765825394\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/fcb47626eee0a0e0d4d5a789ec5d3baa.webm?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/fcb47626eee0a0e0d4d5a789ec5d3baa.mp4?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在完成您晚上的最后一次送货路线时，探索各种独特的房屋和地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/b94010f85d5b83bc62756d500d50fb32.poster.avif?t=1765825394\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/b94010f85d5b83bc62756d500d50fb32.webm?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/b94010f85d5b83bc62756d500d50fb32.mp4?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完成任务:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将水壶送到指定的投递点，找到并归还空壶，并从房主那里收取钱款。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/4893b8eda6fe0a770cad5a4e737a7ad8.poster.avif?t=1765825394\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/4893b8eda6fe0a770cad5a4e737a7ad8.webm?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077670/extras/4893b8eda6fe0a770cad5a4e737a7ad8.mp4?t=1765825394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小心:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你永远不知道下一个转角会有什么在等待你。</p>",
